    "The results of this experiment are presented in Table 2.",
    "It is observed that for the categories of application, material, characterization method, and descriptor, the level of disagreement between the assigned tag and the model-defined tag is below 6 percent.",
    "For the synthesis and symmetry phase label categories, this number is higher but still less than 30% all entities in the category.",
    "It is important to note that certain entities may be difficult to strictly categorize as one or the other NER tag, hence such behavior is expected.",
    "However, a complete understanding of entities requires the consideration of multiple NER tags to capture the different aspects of the entity's characteristics."
